{"tid":306630,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"想買hot toys 已停既 figure","createTime":"2017-07-02T16:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T11:15:54.000Z","uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"066d69bded40d995e3506be35543a88ef54764b9","tid":306630,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"之前男朋友話好鍾意奇異博士嗰隻figure （ 唔係q版我唔知比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n我諗住去買做紀念日禮物， 點知原來hot toys 係根據電影而推出figure， 已經冇得訂買唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店員話可能要等下套戲，最快都18年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （ 因為我男朋友係鍾意個主角多過個角色） 我唔熟識figure，所以好多野都唔知， 想問下會唔會有人拎返出嚟炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我去現時點睇過，但男朋友話入面會有淘寶貨， 有冇人可以教埋我點分辨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42ad9ffdefd08a7516a1857e7f7c0f44b4ef243","tid":306630,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d85f3fee35a286f5dff6999db6dd9cf07fc7b00","tid":306630,"uid":106413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"上facebook search hottoys 會有買賣group<br />\n自己開post 等人pm"},{"pid":"999bb78859eb3044e9ddf26325d29526352f081c","tid":306630,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上facebook search hottoys 會有買賣group<br />\n自己開post 等人pm</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝謝"},{"pid":"bbb8e576e4429af9c212ec471dae236e59be7c40","tid":306630,"uid":41922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"都未派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b964399ece330bd31b36f4a32dc