/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65f8f38f6e0eb5145117a171a5fd8e512399192","tid":306630,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"我連派貨係咩都唔知啊sorry各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec22b1b45a5a9b10fa18e0b48424c131fc56506","tid":306630,"uid":7737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我連派貨係咩都唔知啊sorry各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHot toys既野全部都係訂左貨先<br />\n訂完貨出貨再通知你叫你去拎<br />\n你打去問下隻野截左訂未先啦 或者上網收張訂單 到時派貨再去拎咪得"},{"pid":"c21244dc8223201dd3fae87c1f04e99ebf1a79c8","tid":306630,"uid":109159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:07:19.000Z","msg":"正常Hottoys賣玩具呢都會有段時間俾人去落訂<br />\n訂左呢就未攞得住嘅<br />\n要等佢派 <br />\n幾時派就隻隻唔定嘅 只有鳩等<br />\n咁樓主想買嗰隻奇異博士呢<br />\n早排就開左釘(即第一句)<br />\n咁而家就過左冇得再訂啦<br />\n職員同你講叫你等第二集出左再訂呢就係廢話黎<br />\n唔撚洗理佢<br />\n咁由於hottoys 仲未派貨<br />\n大家都等緊<br />\n所以樓主現階段係冇可能買到嘅<br />\n所以建議你買shf嗰隻奇異博士(見圖)<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/130717_82fc89d81fcf0db281ba0e26bba75957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F130717_82fc89d81fcf0db281ba0e26bba75957.jpg&h=79751f6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f12dbda82c519064dcc3036771d54aa62e7be557","tid":306630,"uid":123034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"到時y拍大把啦。"},{"pid":"224bdaff65ea462c304973f4b4b1ced0e5f742cb","tid":306630,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"多謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif